                        <i class="bi bi-globe feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3 class="h4">Sustainability</h3>
                        <p>
                            Committed to environmentally friendly solutions that protect our land for future generations.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-people feature-icon"></i>
